response.summary: Beispielfirma GmbH issues an invoice to Frau Müller for utensils (forks, knives, spoons) with quantities, unit prices, and totals. The itemized net amount is 275.00 EUR, VAT 19% 52.25 EUR, bringing the total to 327.25 EUR, with payment due by 25.05.2015 to the listed bank account. The document includes invoice number RE-2013-12345, customer number 12345, and dates such as Datum 11.05.2015 and Rechnungsdatum 11.05.2023, indicating potential date inconsistencies. Contact person Manuela Schmidt and the Beispielfirma address are provided.
response.title: Invoice from Beispielfirma
